In some way, the microbe uses arsenic as a survival resource, and taking this ability into account, the chances increase that there could be similar life on other planets that do not have our protective atmosphere.
When these organisms metabolize the arsenic, according to astrobiologists, it is proven that "there is actually another life form, a second life form, which is different from the one known to us."
